Hi Team, I wanted to inform you that I've made updates to the new service onboarding document. It now includes instructions on updating the vulnerability service-to-team mapping. This step is crucial for the assignment of Vulnerability Jira Issues and maintaining security compliance. Kindly review the details outlined in the Enterprise Compliance guidelines and please ensure to follow them.
